  <summary date="2022-04-01T20:58:15Z" status="Introduced in House">National Climate Service Corps and Careers Network Act of 2021

This bill establishes the Climate Resiliency Service Corps as a national service program to assist communities in mitigating the effects climate change and establishes the Climate Careers Network to connect individuals with jobs in green industries.</summary>
